name: The Rescued Galgoz
description: I like to create imaginary worlds where things are just as I imagine. In my happy imaginary world, a bunch of cute, rocker and rescued greyhound dogs, get together to create a rock band. Yes. Why not? They feel great cause they have a new family, they don’t run marathons for assholes anymore. They have a lot of spear time and they love music, so they follow their true dream which is being part of a rock band.
